You are working on GridMind EPC™, a luxury enterprise utility-scale solar design and SCADA platform.

Architecture:
- web/ is the Next.js 14 app for Vercel.
- supabase/schema.sql is the database source of truth.
- Python Streamlit/FastAPI legacy files remain for local Docker demos.
- New production development should prioritize Next.js, Supabase, and Vercel.

Coding rules:
- Keep engineering formulas deterministic and unit-tested.
- Do not hardcode secrets. Use environment variables only.
- Use Supabase Row Level Security for user-owned and authenticated data.
- Keep UI premium, clean, technical, and suitable for enterprise EPC clients.
- Every new calculation must include units in names and labels.
- Preserve GridMind EPC™ branding: navy #002B49, orange #FF8C00, mist #F4F6F8.
